"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/18/8b/a7/b6471f02.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1662528250,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1662528250","product_id":100038501,"comment_content":"如何推动干系人进行干系人领域任务，我们项目也是遇到文中一样的境遇，我们项目当前的瓶颈就是设计人员，设计人员事情太多，忙不过来进行设计，项目迟迟无法推进，项目组成员没有实质性工作可以进行，这种情况怎么处理？","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":343088,"user_name":"木白","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":2981592,"ip_address":"","ucode":"EE7E1925473C77","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/2d/7e/d8/b7ed8970.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1650621856,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1650621856","product_id":100038501,"comment_content":"很多时候项目都是打关系，或者销售占主导地位。没有什么发挥空间","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":337920,"user_name":"森林木","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1220089,"ip_address":"","ucode":"79A06FCC43673B","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/12/9d/f9/b98d9c40.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1647158921,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1647158921","product_id":100038501,"comment_content":"个人感觉是执行过程中项目组成员有的时候也是要花比较多时间管理的，尤其是大厂，大家都比较优秀有各自的想法，这方面的管理成本不知道如何很好地控制。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":305920,"user_name":"周文玲","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":2717044,"ip_address":"","ucode":"DA071849C9743E","user_header":"","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1628231404,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1628231404","product_id":100038501,"comment_content":"面对甲方项目经理责任大，权力小时，根本不让你接触到高层一点的干系人，一直都在基层干系人间徘徊，且没有办法去决定需求的范围，并不是满足了他们的需求就能让项目得到一个正向结果，最终都是不停的范围蔓延，沟通成本和各种风险都很高，项目人的每日艰难","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":301291,"user_name":"磉盘","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1055624,"ip_address":"","ucode":"1C245991F30A73","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/1b/88/ac69f57a.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1625623004,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1625623004","product_id":100038501,"comment_content":"每个大型项目都需要多人参与，对项目进度有直接和间接影响的都属于干系人，有了主次关系人自然利益也就不同了。有人支持项目的进展，有人无所谓，更甚者有不支持项目的发展，项目推进如多人合理推车上坡，只有力往一处使才能快速上坡。<br><br>人多想法也多，要想统一大家想法，就需要针对性地对待其诉求和期望，让所有人对项目产生积极的影响，从而更好地保障项目目标的成功达成。<br><br>干系人对项目的权利和利益，四象限基本上可以囊括所有的人，针对干系人进行规划管理。高权高利，重点管理、高权低利，使其满意、高利低权，随时告知、低权低利，监控进展符合预期。<br><br>","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":289724,"user_name":"陈林","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":2496862,"ip_address":"","ucode":"5305EAD9823969","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/26/19/5e/89d4aee7.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1619155533,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1619155533","product_id":100038501,"comment_content":"我感觉，很多时候开发的能力和思想方向需要疏导，有时候协调各方问题，找到最大公约数<br>设计经理这个案例我觉得很棒","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":288544,"user_name":"小芝麻","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1665325,"ip_address":"","ucode":"7EA0F4662C58AD","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/19/69/2d/5afe6921.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1618534893,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1618534893","product_id":100038501,"comment_content":"感觉没有分析过干系人，一般接触较多的是产品和项目组成员，产品：认真了解产品的业务诉求，然后跟进完成开发，项目组成员——同一战线，先各司其职，有问题一起跟进，技术领导层——完成业务诉求的同时，完成技术指标及要求","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":245299,"user_name":"山中千年","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1499008,"ip_address":"","ucode":"D5615B465A6316","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/16/df/80/8308b0eb.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1598887882,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1598887882","product_id":100038501,"comment_content":"一个项目组有产品、前台、后台等等组成，那这些岗位的负责人，比如后台负责人，属于哪个类型呢？感觉他们权力也高利益也不低啊","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":241522,"user_name":"吴志平","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":2093588,"ip_address":"","ucode":"A5BC90E11AD2FC","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/1f/f2/14/616ecc65.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1597321861,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1597321861","product_id":100038501,"comment_content":"驱动团队和个人前进的不仅仅只有权力和利益，为什么只从利益和权力两个维度对干系人分类呢？这种分类方式为什么合理？","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":220103,"user_name":"橘子龙","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1112359,"ip_address":"","ucode":"8F39025CCB4123","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/f9/27/2f71dbbe.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1590157767,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1590157767","product_id":100038501,"comment_content":"这里是不是说把项目参与人分一下类 以便项目过程中知道找谁","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":217864,"user_name":"舒偌一","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1053833,"ip_address":"","ucode":"C1F87ED4E84FD9","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/14/89/229bb890.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1589634095,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1589634095","product_id":100038501,"comment_content":"我认为能管理的只有自己和项目信息，需要做的是充分利用这些信息服务各干系人。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":204996,"user_name":"牺牲","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1619402,"ip_address":"","ucode":"5780E562A43494","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/18/b5/ca/bba4d696.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1586505184,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":2,"score":"1586505184","product_id":100038501,"comment_content":"针对目前的招聘工作，我的身份处在低利益-高权力的代表职能经理，并且是支持者。<br>我的问题是团队和团队之间沟通频次低，信息不同步，没有计划完成时间和进度安排，缺少保证实现的措施和变通方案；潜在风险是现成员的离职，最大的风险是长时间招不到人，岗位空缺影响业务推动。<br>我希望项目管理可以确定计划完成日期，实时关注招聘进度并同步，根据阶段问题制定解决方案，针对各类风险制定变通方案。<br>根据表中的问题回答完后 ，我针对问题再贴上自己的想法，就可以向上反馈了。我希望我可以起到有力的推动作用，而不是只让管理者自己负责。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":167700,"user_name":"luqh","can_delete":false,"prod